name: Syrup x Kaas Party Jacket
description:
A cosmic collaboration between the holographic-heads of the SYRUP & YAYO squad and the wavy weave-work of KAAS Leisurewear has given new light to the concept of futuristic nostalgia. We have brought to you; a limited edition limb-flailing themed, lightweight jacket and tee release, all designed around the MDNGHT TL DYLGHT poster premise by Hand Studio. Stock is very limited and there is no plans for re-orders so please get in early to avoid disappointment. 
See you in the clubhouz

Black/Black outer, Custom artwork hood and pocket lining, 100% Down Proof Cotton, Pouch pocket with zip on front, diagonal side pockets, adjustable hood, genuine leather tag on pouch.

Model wears Large.
